OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late brightness
OL,7,Fin places. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be mainly dry but the odd shower
OL,9,Fpossible in the north later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FChance of a light shower in
OL,12,Fthe north at first. Otherwise dry with
OL,13,Fsome sunshine by afternoon. Patchy
OL,14,Flight rain in the evening. Warm.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,17,Fon Saturday with outbreaks of rain
OL,18,Fspreading southeast at times. A few
OL,19,Fearly showers on Sunday otherwise dry.
OL,20,FFurther cloud and rain spreading east
OL,21,Fon Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
